      "note": "Open CASCADE BREP files start with 'CASCADE Topology V1, (c) Matra Datavision' or a similar header. This is a strong, unique identifier for OCCT BREP format, distinguishing it from Parasolid BREP (X_T/X_B) and ACIS SAT."
    }
  },
  "variables": {
    "brepHeader": "",
