  "aiHints": {
    "analysisContext": "Open CASCADE BREP ASCII format. Structure: header line 'CASCADE Topology V1, (c) Matra Datavision\\n', then sections: locations_count\\nN_location_records (4x4 matrix each), curves_count\\nN_curve_records, 2d_curves_count\\nN_2d_curve_records, surfaces_count\\nN_surface_records, polygons_on_triangulation_count\\nN_POT_records, triangulations_count\\nN_triangulation_records, then TopoDS shape records (compound/compsolid/solid/shell/face/wire/edge/vertex with flags and references). Curve types: 1=Line, 2=Circle, 3=Ellipse, 4=Hyperbola, 5=Parabola, 6=BezierCurve, 7=BSplineCurve, 8=TrimmedCurve, 9=OffsetCurve. Surface types: 1=Plane, 2=Cylinder, 3=Cone, 4=Sphere, 5=Torus, 6=LinearExtrusion, 7=Revolution, 8=Bezier, 9=BSpline, 10=RectSurf, 11=OffsetSurf.",
    "suggestedInspections": [
      "Line 1: 'CASCADE Topology V1, (c) Matra Datavision' confirms Open CASCADE BREP",
      "After header sections: count values before each geometry section (locations, curves, surfaces)",
      "Shape tree at end: TopoDS hierarchy with face/edge/vertex references to geometry",
      "Triangulation sections: mesh data for visualization (separate from exact B-rep)"
    ]
  },
